4cc9e4ca.data: The first draft is just you telling yourself the story.

61d02558.data: You can not wait for inspiration. You have to go after it with a club.

89b44cb5.data: I write to be the characters that I am not. I write to explore all the things I am afraid of.

70123c3e.data: I must write it all out, at any cost. Writing is thinking. It is more than living, for it is being conscious of living.

309c4453.data: Words are our most inexhaustible source of magic.

47524e75.data: The true alchemists do not change lead into gold; they change the world into words.

884124bc.data: I went for years not finishing anything. Because, of course, when you finish something you can be judged.

5e91ed42.data: I love deadlines. I like the whooshing sound they make as they fly by.

20805818.data: Write your first draft with your heart. Rewrite with your head.
